091F3DEE.Line13.6E261: (scoff) How many messages did I send, huh? How long has Oyuun been missing, trapped in there with those butchers?

27FCB7D0.Line7.6D03F: Gone to the palace, no doubt. Behind the High Wall with the gates barred behind him. We can’t get through.

47AE6E2E.Line31.6E261: She may be the only one left who knows of the tunnel!

5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: Good of you to come. Pity you didn’t bring an army. Or siegeworks.

8F558C51.Line25.6E261: She has a house in the Market Square. We were supposed to meet there before, but I couldn’t get close.

A313225F.Line15.6D03F: If she’s still alive. If this tunnel exists at all.

B2324D17.Line23.BAE4: If I were to look for Oyuun, where would I start?

D6FC1563.Line19.6D03F: Of course not, you’re a thief. Useful years ago, true, but it’s clear you have some other reason to seek this “Oyuun”.
